<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="occasionally-adv">occasionally <strong><em>adv</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /ə'keɪʒnəli/    美 /ə'keɪʒnəli/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>偶尔；间或：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Occasionally, I would read a novel that was assigned, but I didn't enjoy this type of reading.
偶尔我会读（老师）布置的小说，但我不喜欢这种类型的读物。</p><footer>2019天津</footer></div>

<h2 id="_2">真题解析</h2>
<ol>
<li>I’ve been writing this report <strong><em>_</em></strong>_ (occasional) for the last two weeks, but it has to be handed in tomorrow.  （2011 浙江改）  </li>
</ol>
<p>答案：
1. occasionally  </p></div>